  "text": "We will vary the number of levels, gates in each level, and types of gates, and assign gates to many circuit levels in order to optimize the evolution process. We investigate the fact shown in [CITATION_1] that evolving some circuits is easier to do on a larger scanning window, but this has resulted in a less efficient circuit.",
